metadata.name: The Great March of Humanity
metadata.description:
In this collage, I tried to express our walks in search of our place, our dreams, our goals.
We are all in search of what makes us happy, each in their own way, using what they have available.
Some obstacles will always appear along the way, but that's what makes this journey even more special, because overcoming these obstacles, we learn a little more about life...
